oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Edgehill Urban Renewal Area, 10th Avenue South Looking North from Rose Park Hill, 1965
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Photograph of 10th Avenue South looking north from Rose Park Hill, 26 August 1965. The area was part of the Edgehill Urban Renewal Project area (Project Tenn. R-69). Photographed by Bill Driver of the Nashville Housing Authority. Forms part of the MDHA Photograph Collection. 1 photograph : b & w.
